# Cloud Build / gcloud source upload exclusions.
#
# WHY this exists separately from .gitignore:
# .gitignore excludes runs/*/work/ (training scratch + checkpoints) so
# they don't get committed. But the production YOLO weights live at
# runs/yolo_curve_n16/work/runs/hockeyai_shot_n16/weights/best.pt and
# the audio weights at runs/audio_curve_n16/work/best.pt — both need to
# reach Cloud Build to get baked into the container image. Without
# this file gcloud falls back to .gitignore, drops the weights, and
# the Dockerfile's sanity check fails the build.
#
# Same content lives at .dockerignore so the build steps inside the
# Docker daemon also see the same view.

# ── Python / build junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
build/
dist/

# ── OS junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Git ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore
.github/

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
log/
*.log

# ── Raw video data (gigabytes) ──────────────────────────────────────
data/videos/

# ── Cached per-second features (regenerable, big) ───────────────────
data/output/yolo_features/
data/output/audio_features/

# ── Pipeline-run output dumps (per-run scratch) ─────────────────────
data/output/runs/
data/output/wav/

# ── Training data ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
data/labels/images/
runs/*/dataset/

# runs/*/work/ holds production weights (best.pt) alongside training
# scratch (results.csv, plots, val frames). Total per-run is ~100MB.
# We need the weights baked into the image, and the complex re-include
# patterns to exclude scratch+keep weights are too fragile in gitignore
# syntax. Just ship the whole thing — 100MB is cheap, image stays
# ~1-2 GB regardless.

# ── Local-only customer copies + symlinks ───────────────────────────
/CUST*.json
/customerID_*.json
data/customers/customerID_*.json

# ── Heavy archives ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# ── Coach-facing scratch ────────────────────────────────────────────
candidate_output/

# ── Misc ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
testbild.png
models/
